---
title: Jamaican Chicken Tacos with Charred Corn Salsa & Garlic Aioli
description: You told us you loved Jamaican jerk chicken, and we listened! We're giving it a spin in tasty tacos with a tangy corn salsa and crunchy lettuce to bring the meal together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/jamaican-chicken-tacos-3121ad0f.jpg
